[All Enemies Gone (except bosses?)]
author=bungholio
description=It&#039;s a different value for the codejunkies difficulty code. It probably saves too. The final boss, Walter, didn&#039;t disappear though, so the few bosses might stay. Change it to a normal difficulty when you need to. 04 is also a difficulty, looks like a very hard difficulty because enemies are a bit quicker and hit even faster.
patch=1,EE,0045ADF4,extended,00000005

