[Avoid Enemy Attacks (rotate beneath floor, press L3)]
author=bungholio
description=I think Henry&#039;s pitch, yaw, and roll values are at 2045A5C0, 2045A5C8, and 2045A5D0, or at least very close to that. It resets itself everytime you enter a room. I set it so Henry rotates and ends up upside down below the floor. Enemies can&#039;t hit you and you can go through doors and do everything else you normally can except for hit enemies.
Yeah, it&#039;s kind of a dumb way to avoid enemies, but it works and I can&#039;t find another way.

Joker from CMGSCCC.
patch=1,EE,D1F12EC2,extended,0000FFFD
patch=1,EE,2045A5C0,extended,41800000

[Better Camera Zoom]
author=bungholio
description=smaller number = zoom farther out, try 3e800000. Everything closer to the center of the screen gets farther away.
bigger number = zoom in more.
patch=1,EE,10B0C286,extended,00001622

