[Move Through Walls (Hold L2 and any direction)]
author=bungholio
description=What it specifically does is modify your current location. Holding L2 and either down or left will pull you to the center of the room at either the X or Y axis. Holding L2 and either up or right will move you away from the center of the room exponentially farther away, so you won&#039;t need to hold it for long.

You can also use it to get away from enemies very fast.

Joker from CMGSCCC.
